        "heading": "\"All Salons Need Good Karma\"<br>\n\nKarma Salon Furniture is a family-founded and operated business based on the Gold Coast, Queensland. Established at the end of 2020, we have defied the odds and have been bringing Good Karma to salons across Australia ever since.\n\nOur mission is to provide quality, stylish, and functional furniture to every salon, barbershop, and beauty space. With over 30 years of combined industry experience, our founders, Karl and Maher, have their fingers firmly on the pulse of the hair and beauty industry. Their shared passion for both barbering and hairdressing has made them respected leaders in the trade, with the knowledge and expertise to understand what’s trending, what’s evolving, and what’s here to stay.\n\nAt Karma Salon Furniture, sustainability is at the heart of what we do. Because we design and manufacture our own furniture, we have a deep understanding of every piece we create. We believe in repairing rather than replacing wherever possible, allowing us to provide lasting solutions instead of temporary fixes. Our commitment to quality, longevity, and customer support ensures that every piece of Karma furniture is built to serve your salon for years to come.",
