        "faq_iBAtFG": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "FAQs",
            "description": "Find answers to your questions.",
            "icon": "info",
            "popup_info": "<h3>What is the estimated delivery time for my order?</h3><p>Our standard delivery time is 5-10 business days, depending on your location. We’ll keep you updated with tracking information so you can monitor your order’s progress.</p><h3>Do you offer assembly services?</h3><p>Yes, we offer an optional assembly service for most items. During checkout, you can choose this option to have our team handle setup upon delivery.</p><h3>What is your return policy if I’m not satisfied with my purchase?</h3><p>We accept returns within 30 days of delivery for a full refund or exchange, as long as the item is in its original condition. Please contact our customer service team to initiate a return.</p><h3>What should I do if my order arrives damaged or incomplete?</h3><p>We’re here to help. Please reach out to our customer service team with your order number and photos of the issue, and we’ll work quickly to resolve it—whether that means a replacement, refund, or missing item follow-up.</p><h3>Will sold-out items be restocked, and how can I get notified?</h3><p>We frequently restock our bestsellers. To stay updated on restocks and new arrivals, we recommend subscribing to our newsletter—you’ll be the first to know.<br/><br/></p>"
          }
        },
